PREFIX dbpedia-owl: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX dbpedia-owl: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT DISTINCT ?plant_resource_field_plant_thumbnail ?plant_resource_field_plant_label ?plant_resource_field_plant_abstract ?plant_resource WHERE { ?plant_resource dbpedia-owl:family <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Poaceae>; dbpedia-owl:kingdom <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Plant>; dbpedia-owl:thumbnail ?plant_resource_field_plant_thumbnail; rdfs:label ?plant_resource_field_plant_label; dbpedia-owl:abstract ?plant_resource_field_plant_abstract. FILTER langMatches(lang(?plant_resource_field_plant_abstract), "EN") FILTER langMatches(lang(?plant_resource_field_plant_label), "EN") } LIMIT 20

PREFIX foaf: <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/> PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> SELECT ?manufacturer ?name ?car WHERE { ?car <http://purl.org/dc/terms/subject> <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Category:Luxury_vehicles> . ?car foaf:name ?name . ?car dbo:manufacturer ?man . ?man foaf:name ?manufacturer FILTER regex(?name,'Toyota') }

PREFIX foaf: <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/> PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> SELECT ?manufacturer ?name ?car WHERE { ?car <http://purl.org/dc/terms/subject> <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Category:Luxury_vehicles> . ?car foaf:name ?name . ?car dbo:manufacturer ?man . ?man foaf:name ?manufacturer FILTER regex(?name,'Lexus') }

PREFIX dcterms: <http://purl.org/dc/terms/> PREFIX dbpedia: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> select * where { dbpedia:Assay dcterms:subject ?Subject. ?Subject rdfs:label ?Techniques. filter regex(?Techniques,"Laboratory techniques"). ?Assay dcterms:subject ?Subject. }

PREFIX dbpprop: <http://dbpedia.org/property/> PREFIX foaf: <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/> PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> PREFIX dbpedia: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX dbpedia: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX dbpediaowl: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX foaf: <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/> PREFIX dbpprop: <http://dbpedia.org/property/> SELECT ?surname (group_concat(?instname ; separator = ";") AS ?instrumentsplayed) WHERE { dbpedia:Daft_Punk dbpediaowl:bandMember ?person . ?person foaf:surname ?surname . ?person dbpprop:instrument ?instruments . ?instruments rdfs:label ?instname . FILTER(langMatches(lang(?instname), "EN")) } GROUP BY ?surname

PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX dbp: <http://dbpedia.org/property/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT ?album ?albumName ?rdate WHERE {?song dbo:producer <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Timbaland>; dbo:album ?album; dbp:releaseDate ?rdate. ?album rdfs:label ?albumName. FILTER(datatype(?rdate)=xsd:date). }

PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX res: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> SELECT ?ime ?dataRaganje ?mestoNaraganje ?dataDeath ?mestoUmiranje WHERE { res:The_Little_Prince dbo:author ?name. ?name dbo:birthName ?ime. ?name dbo:birthDate ?dataRaganje . ?name dbo:birthPlace ?mestoraganje. ?mestoraganje rdfs:label ?mestoNaraganje. ?name dbo:deathDate ?dataDeath. ?name dbo:deathPlace ?smrt. ?smrt rdfs:label ?mestoUmiranje. FILTER (lang(?mestoNaraganje)="en") }

PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX res: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> SELECT ?ime ?data ?mest WHERE { res:The_Little_Prince dbo:author ?name. ?name dbo:birthName ?ime. ?name dbo:birthDate ?data. ?name dbo:birthPlace ?mestoraganje. ?mestoraganje rdfs:label ?mestoNaraganje FILTER (lang(?mest)="en") }

SELECT ?deathPlace ?birthPlace ?bio ?image ?death ?birth WHERE { <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josquin_des_Prez> <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/birthDate> ?birth ; <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/birthPlace> ?birthP ; <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/deathDate> ?death ; <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/deathPlace> ?deathP ; <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/depiction> ?image ; <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/abstract> ?bio . ?birthP <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> ?birthPlace . ?deathP <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> ?deathPlace . FILTER ( langmatches( lang( ?birthPlace), "en") ) FILTER ( langmatches( lang( ?deathPlace), "en") ) FILTER ( langmatches( lang( ?bio), "en") ) }

PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> select ?album ?albumName ?date where { ?album dbo:producer <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Timbaland>. ?album rdfs:label ?albumName. FILTER(lang(?albumName)='en') ?album dbo:releaseDate ?date . FILTER(datatype(?date)=xsd:date) } order by ASC(?date)

PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX dbp: <http://dbpedia.org/property/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX dbp: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> Select ?ime ?dataRaganje ?mesto ?dataUmiranje ?umiranje WHERE{ dbp:The_Little_Prince dbo:author ?name . ?name dbo:birthName ?ime . ?name dbo:birthDate ?dataRaganje . ?name dbo:birthPlace ?mestoRaganje . ?mestoRaganje rdfs:label ?mesto . ?name dbo:deathDate ?dataUmiranje . ?name dbo:deathPlace ?mestoUmiranje . ?mestoUmiranje rdfs:label ?umiranje. FILTER (lang(?mesto)="en") FILTER (lang(?umiranje)="en") }
